Import & Export

Global Supply & Distribution

At PTCGRAM Private Limited, we are engaged in the import and export of high-quality industrial chemicals and raw materials. With a strong supplier and logistics network, we ensure safe handling, compliant packaging, and timely delivery across international markets.

Our Import Services

We import high-quality chemicals and raw materials from trusted global manufacturers to meet the growing demand of Indian industries.

Imported Products Include:
	•	Industrial solvents
	•	Specialty chemicals
	•	Acids and alkalis
	•	Fragrance and essential oil raw materials
	•	Cleaning chemical raw materials

Our Export Services

We export a wide range of industrial and specialty chemicals to international clients with proper documentation and compliance.

Export Products Include:
	•	Caustic Soda
	•	Industrial chemicals
	•	Cleaning chemical concentrates
	•	Solvents and raw materials
	•	Essential oils and fragrances

Packaging & Compliance
	•	UN Approved Packaging (for hazardous chemicals)
	•	Fumigation certification when required
	•	Dangerous Goods Declaration (DGD)
	•	MSDS documentation
	•	Custom export packaging

Logistics & Documentation

We handle complete export documentation including:
	•	Commercial Invoice
	•	Packing List
	•	Certificate of Origin
	•	MSDS & Technical Data Sheets
	•	Dangerous Goods Declaration (if applicable)
	•	Shipping via sea, air, or road transport

Markets We Serve

We aim to supply chemicals to markets including:
	•	Middle East
	•	Southeast Asia
	•	Africa
	•	South Asia

